@startuml
title Download Lifecycle
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> queued : create job/item
queued --> running : worker picks item
running --> succeeded : download completes
running --> failed : unrecoverable error
running --> paused : user pauses
queued --> paused : user pauses before worker
queued --> cancelled : user cancels
running --> cancelled : cancel requested
paused --> queued : restart
failed --> queued : restart
succeeded --> queued : restart
cancelled --> queued : restart
queued --> [*] : delete
running --> [*] : delete
paused --> [*] : delete
failed --> [*] : delete
succeeded --> [*] : delete
cancelled --> [*] : delete

note right of running
Progress is aggregated across yt-dlp
sub-stream payloads and remains monotonic.
end note
@enduml
